{"parentUuid":"44329b73-1d9f-41dd-8247-dee1d85cef81","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/so/MyWorkSpace/personal/care-inomi","sessionId":"7971e18e-d35e-4d71-b55b-b0375fbc3ac1","version":"2.1.19","gitBranch":"develop","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-5-20251101","id":"msg_01EJ9pcmWxvfR1orDtwiwK6K","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"ユーザーはCloudflare PagesとGitHubを連携して、以下のワークフローを構築したいと考えている：\n\n1. developブランチ → Cloudflare非本番環境（プレビュー）へデプロイ\n2. 動作確認\n3. mainブランチ → Cloudflare本番環境へデプロイ\n\nこれはCloudflare Pagesの標準的な機能で実現できる。調べて回答する。","signature":""}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":28384,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":28384,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":6,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CXULbpX7i3roWvooE15cW","type":"assistant","uuid":"2298a567-2230-4459-a8b8-2e0fcd81439d","timestamp":"2026-01-25T15:32:52.875Z"}
{"parentUuid":"2298a567-2230-4459-a8b8-2e0fcd81439d","isSidechain":false,"userType":"external","cwd":"/Users/so/MyWorkSpace/personal/care-inomi","sessionId":"7971e18e-d35e-4d71-b55b-b0375fbc3ac1","version":"2.1.19","gitBranch":"develop","message":{"model":"claude-opus-4-5-20251101","id":"msg_01EJ9pcmWxvfR1orDtwiwK6K","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Cloudflare Pagesの標準機能で実現できます。\n\n## セットアップ手順\n\n### 1. Cloudflare PagesでGitHub連携\n\n1. [Cloudflare Dashboard](https://dash.cloudflare.com/) → **Workers & Pages** → **Create**\n2. **Connect to Git** → GitHubアカウント認証 → リポジトリ選択\n3. ビルド設定：\n   - **Production branch**: `main`\n   - **Framework preset**: Astro\n   - **Build command**: `npm run build`\n   - **Build output directory**: `dist`\n\n### 2. ブランチデプロイの動作\n\n設定完了後、自動的に以下の動作になる：\n\n| ブランチ | デプロイ先 | URL |\n|---------|-----------|-----|\n| `main` | 本番環境 | `your-project.pages.dev` |\n| `develop` | プレビュー環境 | `develop.your-project.pages.dev` |\n| `feature/*` | プレビュー環境 | `feature-xxx.your-project.pages.dev` |\n\n### 3. 推奨ワークフロー\n\n```\nfeature/* → develop（プレビューで動作確認）→ main（本番デプロイ）\n```\n\n1. `develop`にマージ → 自動でプレビュー環境にデプロイ\n2. `develop.your-project.pages.dev` で動作確認\n3. 確認OK → `develop`から`main`へPR作成・マージ\n4. 自動で本番環境にデプロイ\n\n### 4. 追加設定（任意）\n\n**Preview deployments の制限**（Settings → Builds → Branch deployments）：\n- **Production branch**: `main`\n- **Preview branches**: `develop` のみに限定も可能\n\n**環境変数の分離**（Settings → Variables）：\n- Production用とPreview用で別々の環境変数を設定可能\n\nこれで `develop` → プレビュー確認 → `main` → 本番 のフローが自動化されます。"}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":10,"cache_creation_input_tokens":28384,"cache_read_input_tokens":0,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":28384,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":0},"output_tokens":6,"service_tier":"standard"}},"requestId":"req_011CXULbpX7i3roWvooE15cW","type":"assistant","uuid":"80550fc3-882b-4596-abd5-ace864be7ede","timestamp":"2026-01-25T15:33:02.546Z"}
